These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, iris, aconite, balloon-flower
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, lawyer, analyst, project-manager
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, emerald, red, light-blue
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games, fishing, card-games
 1. the security-guard is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
 2. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 3. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who likes light-blue is the lawyer##1
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 6. the security-guard is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 7. the person who likes emerald is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the lawyer##5
 9. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the analyst##3
10. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who growsrose##7
11. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes red##1
12. the project-manager is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
13. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Flower   | balloon-flower    | iris | aconite    | rose   |
| Job   | security-guard | analyst | lawyer | project-manager |
| Color           | emerald       | red   | light-blue  | ivory     |
| Hobby     | filmmaking      | fishing   | card-games    | board-games    |

