.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, gardening, skydiving, puzzles
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk, 7up, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, electronic, hip-hop, r&b
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, september, june, july
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
 2. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the right of the fan r&b##5
 3. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is the fan salsa##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the fan hip-hop##3
 6. the fan electronic is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the fan salsa##7
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
10. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
11. the fan electronic is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby          | woodworking   | skydiving       | puzzles    | gardening      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | sprite | soy-milk         | 7up   |
