4 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, backgammon, scrabble
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, disco, soul, rock
 1. the fan rock is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
 2. the fan rock is somewhere between the person who likes azure and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##7
 3. the person who likes lavender is the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the fan jazz is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
 5. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
 6. the fan jazz is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
 7. the person who likes apricot is not the person who's hobby is camping##6
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person who likes aquamarine##6
 9. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
10. the fan rock is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
11. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
12. the person playing backgammon is the fan soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Color           | aquamarine | azure | lavender | apricot |
