.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, bike, helicopter, scooter
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, old-henry, fonseca, bluemaster
4 different pets are kept: pony, dog, bird, lizard
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, avocado, banana, corn
 1. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is the person driving the train##1
 3. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
 4. the person driving the scooter is the person eating banana##1
 5. the game-smoker is not the person eating cranberry##6
 6. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
 7. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 8. the owner of the dog is somewhere between the old-henry-smoker and the game-smoker##7
 9. the owner of the dog is the person eating cranberry##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
11. the owner of the pony is not the person eating cranberry##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |        3        |      4       |
| Transport      | train | helicopter       | bike         | scooter       |
| Cigar         | game     | bluemaster    | fonseca   | old-henry |
| Pet           | lizard   | dog | bird | pony     |
| Food   | corn      | cranberry          | avocado           | banana |

