4 different games are played: canasta, snooker, domino, monopoly
House: cottage, art-deco, farmhouse, tower
 1. the tower house is the scientist##1
 2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the scientist##1
 3. the scientist is somewhere to the left of the person playing monopoly##5
 4. the person playing domino is on the left of the librarian##1
 5. the scientist is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
 6. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
 7. the scientist is somewhere between the cottage house and the art-deco house##7
 8. the lawyer is not the cottage house##6
 9. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person playing domino##1
11. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
12. the scientist is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Job         | fisherman      | scientist   | lawyer   | librarian       |
| Flower   | begonia | dahlia    | amaryllis | lily       |
| Game   | canasta  | snooker | domino   | monopoly     |
| House         | cottage   | tower    | art-deco   | farmhouse |

