.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, bike, helicopter, trike
House: art-deco, gothic-revival, cottage, tower
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, mystery, sports, scientific
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, pilot, trikecher, project-manager
 1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 2. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5
 3. the person watching scientific movies is between the project-manager and the trikecher##2
 4. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 5. the gothic-revival house is not the pilot##6
 6. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
 7. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the tower house##7
 8. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the trikecher##5
 9. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
10. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
11. the person driving the scooter is the cottage house##1
12. the cottage house is not the trikecher##6

.:: Answer ::.
