.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
House: futuristic, farmhouse, cottage, colonial
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, amber, aquamarine, emerald
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, august, may, july
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, motorbike, subway
 1. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
 2. the person driving the scooter is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person who's birthday is in october##2
 3. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
 4. the cottage house is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person driving the skateboard is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere between the person who likes emerald and the person who likes chestnut##7
 8. the person driving the scooter is not the person who likes chestnut##6
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is not the person who likes emerald##6
10. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
11. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
12. the person who likes aquamarine is not the farmhouse house##6
13. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
14. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
15. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the colonial house##3

.:: Answer ::.
