.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different games are played: bridge, snooker, chess, poker
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, amber, lavender, apricot
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, raspberry, cabbage, grapefruit
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, orchid, dahlia, balloon-flower
 1. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
 2. the person who likes lavender is the person playing chess##1
 3. the person who growsorchid is the person eating grapefruit##1
 4. the person eating cabbage is between the person playing poker and the person playing snooker##2
 5. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
 6. the person eating zucchini is somewhere between the person who likes lavender and the person playing bridge##7
 7. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the person who likes amber##5
 8. the person eating zucchini is the person who growsiris##1
 9. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
10. the person eating raspberry is on the far right##1
11. the person who growsdahlia is in an even position##4
12. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Game   | poker      | chess     | snooker   | bridge    |
| Color     | apricot | lavender   | amber | white |
| Food     | grapefruit        | cabbage     | zucchini  | raspberry      |
| Flower   | orchid       | balloon-flower | iris   | dahlia    |

 